name: Yin and Yang
description:
Block recreation of the yin/yang with varying background and foreground effects. Controls ->

-press 'b' to change background type
-press 'up arrow' to change background line color
-press 'down arrow' to change background color
-press 'right arrow' to change image shape type
-press 'left arrow' to change image outline color
-press 'x' to change line fill speed
-press 's' to save as png

Enjoy
